title: Annas Unverpacktes
description: An unpackaged store. You could bring your own container or get paper bags there or buy containers in the shop. Sells foods such as legumes, nuts, seeds, pasta, grains, cornflakes, some sweets, and dried fruits, but also laundry and dish washing liquid and bottled juices and water. Most staple foods are vegan, except for some vegetarian chocolates.
